13:11.110 --> 13:12.860
over the past year, lashing out.

13:12.895 --> 13:14.478
Until very recently.

13:14.480 --> 13:15.896
Over the past few weeks,

13:15.948 --> 13:17.698
she's become withdrawn.

13:17.734 --> 13:18.866
Quiet,

13:19.577 --> 13:21.049
well-behaved.

13:22.201 --> 13:23.568
AUGUST: She was planning her escape.

13:23.570 --> 13:25.956
(woman sobbing loudly)

13:38.554 --> 13:40.971
