18:52.043 --> 18:53.091
I want to help.

18:56.004 --> 18:57.082
My name's Elizabeth.

18:57.134 --> 18:57.891
What's yours?

19:00.587 --> 19:01.920
I know you're scared, so I'm just gonna

19:01.972 --> 19:04.132
sit with you until you're
ready to come out, okay?

19:06.260 --> 19:07.759
My house is-is just up that hill.

19:07.811 --> 19:09.895
It's such a beautiful day,

19:09.930 --> 19:11.547
I thought I'd take a walk by the river.

19:11.572 --> 19:13.207
Actually, that's not entirely true.

19:13.259 --> 19:14.496
My husband, he's traveling,

19:14.548 --> 19:16.735
- and it gets so quiet...
- MAN: I got something over there!

19:17.222 --> 19:18.362
