19:50.387 --> 19:51.898
get your dress washed.

19:51.923 --> 19:54.556
And then we can have some food.

19:54.608 --> 19:56.019
How does that sound?

20:04.879 --> 20:06.735
Okay, let's just

20:06.737 --> 20:08.035
