that's gonna make

21:16.223 --> 21:17.605
what you went through

21:17.641 --> 21:18.836
all right.

21:21.311 --> 21:23.942
All I can do is show you

21:24.448 --> 21:27.454
that I will do whatever it takes

21:27.886 --> 21:29.679
to keep you safe.

21:35.707 --> 21:36.824
Boo.

21:39.950 --> 21:41.573
